#MANUAL DEPLOY


# Deploy in Production cluster

###  _cd_ to _deploy_ folder
``` cd deploy ```

### Connect to cluster
```gcloud container clusters get-credentials prod-cluster-01 --zone us-west1-b --project production-228907```

### Deploy platform
Platform api
```helm --set "global.env=prod" upgrade --install platformapi platformapi```

SSH-Auth
```helm --set "global.env=prod" upgrade --install ssh-auth ssh_auth```



#Deploy in staging and dev clusters


## Platform api

Dev :
	```helm --set "global.env=dev" upgrade --install platformapi platformapi```

Staging :
	```helm --set "global.env=staging" upgrade --install platformapi platformapi```


## SSH-Auth

Dev :
	```helm --set "global.env=dev" upgrade --install ssh-auth ssh_auth```

Staging :
	```helm --set "global.env=staging" upgrade --install ssh-auth ssh_auth```
